A serene Buddhist monastery courtyard at golden hour, rendered in Studio Ghibli style with soft watercolor textures and warm amber lighting. In the foreground, a peaceful stone Buddha statue sits in meditation beneath a gnarled old tree with delicate leaves. Behind it, a traditional East Asian temple building with curved eaves. On a weathered wooden table near the Buddha, an open laptop computer glows softly, its screen reflecting on the ancient stone. A small penguin sits contentedly beside the laptop, appearing to meditate alongside the Buddha. Cherry blossom petals drift gently through the air. The scene blends ancient spirituality with modern technology in perfect harmony, emphasizing tranquility and quiet digital revolution.
